text: Den Dekker is a Dutch occupational surname meaning "the thatcher".Dekker, den at the Database of Surnames in The Netherlands. Other, more common forms of the surname are De Decker, De Dekker, and Dekker. Notable people named Den Dekker include: *Matt den Dekker (born 1987), American baseball outfielder *Michelle den Dekker (born 1966), Australian netball player *Nathalie den Dekker (born 1989), Dutch lawyer and beauty queen *Michael DenDekker (born 1961), American (New York) politician ==References== Category:Dutch-language surnames Category:Occupational surnames
